========================================

Two-step automated sync between HOME and WORK machines.

STEP 1 - On HOME machine:
   sync-both.bat backup

   This creates a backup in .docker-backup\
   Copy the entire .docker-backup folder to USB

STEP 2 - On WORK machine:
   Paste .docker-backup folder here
   sync-both.bat restore

   This restores all changes (merge mode)

OPTIONS:
   backup      - Create backup from current machine
   restore     - Apply backup to current machine
   status      - Show current Docker state

EXAMPLE:
   HOME:  sync-both.bat backup
   USB:   Copy .docker-backup to USB
   WORK:  Paste .docker-backup folder
   WORK:  sync-both.bat restore

